hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I do some voluntary work www.magmed.org.pl The United States has thumbed our nose at the world community time and time again, when it comes to any real consideration of mitigating climate catastrophe. I am also sure the U.N. report is dead-on correct. Our legacy generations from now will be seen as cursed plunderers, squabbling among ourselves while ignoring the obvious. Our ideas of “visionaries” are those who develop the newest cell phones.
